<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>LocalFlow — Cara Zhou</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,300;0,6..72,400;0,6..72,500;1,6..72,400;1,6..72,500&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --paper:#f4f1e8; --card:#fbf9f3; --ink:#15130e; --muted:#8a8172;
    --line:#d9d2c2; --accent:#d9481f; --accent2:#e0531d; --navy:#22303f;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Newsreader',serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  .wrap{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(28px,5vw,64px) clamp(20px,5vw,40px)}
  .mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace}
  .eyebrow{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase}
  /* masthead */
  .mast{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:16px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
  .rule{border-top:1px solid var(--ink);margin:14px 0 0}
  /* hero */
  h1{font-size:clamp(46px,9vw,86px);font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-.02em;
    line-height:.98;margin:30px 0 6px}
  .sub{font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(21px,3vw,30px);color:#3a352c;margin:0 0 22px}
  .lede{font-size:clamp(17px,2vw,20px);line-height:1.55;max-width:60ch;color:#2c2820}
  .lede b{color:var(--accent)}
  /* demo */
  figure{margin:34px 0 8px}
  .frame{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;
    padding:14px;box-shadow:0 24px 50px -28px rgba(60,40,20,.5)}
  .frame img{width:100%;display:block;border-radius:6px}
  figcaption{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-top:12px;text-align:center}
  /* grid */
  .cols{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(24px,4vw,48px);margin-top:44px}
  @media(max-width:680px){.cols{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  h2{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:500}
  dl{margin:0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:9px 18px;
    font-size:15px;line-height:1.4}
  dt{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding-top:2px}
  dd{margin:0;color:#26221b}
  ul.notes{list-style:none;margin:0;padding:0}
  ul.notes li{position:relative;padding:0 0 15px 18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.5;
    color:#26221b}
  ul.notes li::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;top:9px;width:6px;height:6px;
    background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%}
  ul.notes b{font-weight:500}
  /* latency */
  .lat{margin-top:44px}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:15px}
  th,td{text-align:left;padding:10px 4px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  th{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);font-weight:400}
  td.n{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;text-align:right;white-space:nowrap}
  .lat .note{font-size:14px;color:#5a5445;margin-top:12px;font-style:italic}
  /* cta */
  .cta{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:40px}
  .btn{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.08em;
    text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;padding:13px 22px;border-radius:6px;
    transition:transform .18s ease,opacity .18s ease;display:inline-block}
  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .btn.solid{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
  .btn.ghost{border:1px solid var(--ink);color:var(--ink)}
  footer{margin-top:52px;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
    font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.14em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="mast">
    <span>Cara Zhou · The Builder</span>
    <span>AI Project · New York · 2026</span>
  </div>
  <div class="rule"></div>

  <div class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--accent);margin-top:26px">Series №III — Build Log</div>
  <h1>LocalFlow</h1>
  <p class="sub">Voice dictation that never leaves your Mac.</p>
  <p class="lede">A from-scratch, fully-local clone of Wispr Flow. Hold a key,
  speak into any app, and get clean punctuated text back — <b>with nothing
  leaving the machine</b>. On-device Whisper for speech, a local LLM for cleanup,
  wired into macOS through low-level event taps.</p>

  <figure>
    <div class="frame"><img src="data:image/gif;base64," alt="LocalFlow dictation demo"></div>
    <figcaption>Hold fn · ramble · the cleaned text lands in the focused app — illustration</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class="cols">
    <div>
      <h2>The Build</h2>
      <dl>
        <dt>Speech→Text</dt><dd>mlx-whisper (large-v3-turbo) on the Apple Silicon GPU</dd>
        <dt>Cleanup</dt><dd>Qwen2.5-3B, served locally by Ollama</dd>
        <dt>Integration</dt><dd>Quartz event taps · clipboard injection · Tk overlay</dd>
        <dt>Languages</dt><dd>Auto-detected; tuned for English / 中文</dd>
        <dt>Privacy</dt><dd>100% offline — no accounts, no telemetry, no upload</dd>
        <dt>Ships as</dt><dd>A native .app; Spotlight-launchable, login item</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Engineering Notes</h2>
      <ul class="notes">
        <li>The <b>fn key is invisible</b> to normal keyboard APIs — captured via a Quartz event tap, filtered to its true keycode so arrow keys don't false-trigger.</li>
        <li>macOS <b>silently disables event taps</b> whose callback runs slow, wedging the recording. Fixed with threaded callbacks, tap-revival, and a physical-key watchdog.</li>
        <li>The ⌥1 shortcut had to be <b>swallowed</b> — it types "¡", which would destroy the very selection being rewritten.</li>
        <li>A small model's <b>guardrails live in code</b>: language sanity-checks and deterministic name corrections run after the LLM, not on trust.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lat">
    <h2>Latency, Measured</h2>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Stage</th><th>Input</th><th style="text-align:right">Time</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Whisper large-v3-turbo</td><td>8.0s audio</td><td class="n">2.38s</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Whisper large-v3-turbo</td><td>1.0s audio</td><td class="n">2.18s</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Qwen2.5-3B cleanup</td><td>132 chars</td><td class="n">0.66s</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="note">1s of audio costs nearly as much as 8s — Whisper pads every clip
    to a 30s window, so latency is fixed by the encoder, not your speech. That's
    what makes streaming the right next optimization.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cta">
    <a class="btn solid" href="https://github.com/carazhou97/LocalFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on GitHub →</a>
    <a class="btn ghost" href="https://github.com/carazhou97/LocalFlow/blob/main/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the write-up →</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <span>LocalFlow · Whisper + Local LLM</span>
    <span>40.7128° N · Est. 2026</span>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
